\n入局後，他望與本地華裔同事合作，建立工作上的默契。當然，作為小數族裔投身消防的成功例子，他亦想鼓勵更多同族人士投考消防員。<br />\n<br />\n加油華生！我地連登仔仲有好多理智既巴打，唔似黃巢佢地咁見到你地膚色就走去屈人係強姦犯，比心機做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:17:47.000Z","msg":"乜撚野4字詞語，成語就成語啦"},{"pid":"a4453a7fddfc0644acd9825f6b0d647a38756771","tid":926123,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:30:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0106a91758d11e649540c0773c6e944e46679b3","tid":926123,"uid":2883,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:39:29.000Z","msg":"原來班蝻唔犯事已經值得吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ea3ee438fb9c9c69f182a2232a921dc399a7db","tid":926123,"uid":2883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:44:41.000Z","msg":"住喺深水埗、土瓜灣、油麻地、元朗、觀塘嘅香港人生命財產日日受威脅，特別係女性，唔通班蝻作奸犯科香港人都唔可以唔鍾意佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁同德國班左膠有咩分別"},{"pid":"d06910ab6aa9c49448031096c7eed2ad1fe1d976","tid":926123,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7eb370d73ada9b7989a818ea25a530e4d9cf89d","tid":926123,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:59:04.000Z","msg":"係有班白痴有支那蝗唔屌走去屌其他有貢獻既人"},{"pid":"98901223707d1d48a19399b4a7edda8abfc2063a","tid":926123,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:20:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64a7a4a6fe160316befd07c692a32cd66200b9ec","tid":926123,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d740bfa0997ab24b8203f2966ec8f9